1
00:01:43,440 --> 00:01:44,199
By the way,

2
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:46,039
are you Thai?

3
00:01:48,440 --> 00:01:49,639
Yeah, I am.

4
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:51,360
Then...

5
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:53,639
how come you speak Thai so well?

6
00:01:55,320 --> 00:01:57,760
My mother is Thai, actually. That's how I learned.

7
00:01:58,679 --> 00:01:59,639
I'm Karn, by the way.

8
00:02:00,360 --> 00:02:01,400
And you are...?

9
00:02:02,519 --> 00:02:06,280
Kita. But you can just call me Q.

10
00:02:07,599 --> 00:02:11,239
Alright then. This round is on me.

11
00:02:11,880 --> 00:02:14,639
To celebrate us finally meeting.

12
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:17,719
Thank you.

13
00:03:10,760 --> 00:03:11,880
You're getting a bit tipsy,Q.

14
00:03:15,239 --> 00:03:16,000
Want me to take you home?

15
00:03:19,079 --> 00:03:19,920
It’s okay.

16
00:03:21,320 --> 00:03:22,519
I can manage.

17
00:03:30,920 --> 00:03:32,320
Thanks for today.

18
00:03:34,079 --> 00:03:36,440
I had a really great time.

19
00:03:39,039 --> 00:03:40,719
I did too.

20
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:44,199
Let's do this again sometime.

21
00:03:48,079 --> 00:03:49,000
See you around.

22
00:03:49,480 --> 00:03:50,280
Sure thing.

23
00:04:40,039 --> 00:04:41,480
(Dad): You've graduated. 

24
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:42,920
It's time to come back to Thailand.

25
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:47,800
(Kita): I want to travel for a bit longer.

26
00:04:49,079 --> 00:04:50,519
(Dad): No. You need to return ASAP.

27
00:04:50,519 --> 00:04:53,400
I've already arranged a job for you.

28
00:04:56,840 --> 00:04:59,719
(Kita): Dad, I'm not ready to come back yet.

29
00:05:00,159 --> 00:05:03,039
(Dad): I’m giving you one week to get ready and fly home.

30
00:05:20,119 --> 00:05:23,000
(Karn): Good night :)

31
00:05:49,320 --> 00:05:50,800
Smells amazing. Is it ready yet?

32
00:05:51,239 --> 00:05:52,079
Just finished.

33
00:05:52,280 --> 00:05:53,000
Hurry up!

34
00:05:54,159 --> 00:05:55,360
Here you go.

35
00:05:55,519 --> 00:05:56,119
Put it down right here.

36
00:05:58,280 --> 00:05:59,039
Does it look good?

37
00:05:59,239 --> 00:05:59,840
So good!

38
00:06:01,159 --> 00:06:01,800
Let’s eat.

39
00:06:05,719 --> 00:06:06,440
Now this is what I'm talking about.

40
00:06:07,039 --> 00:06:07,760
Delicious!

41
00:06:10,320 --> 00:06:11,119
I’m so jealous of you.

42
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:13,360
Your parents actually understand you.

43
00:06:14,280 --> 00:06:14,780
Why?

44
00:06:16,519 --> 00:06:17,920
You want to transition like me now?

45
00:06:19,840 --> 00:06:20,559
Shut up! 

46
00:06:22,079 --> 00:06:25,559
I mean I'm jealous they accept you for who you are.

47
00:06:27,280 --> 00:06:28,000
Look at me.

48
00:06:28,760 --> 00:06:32,119
I stepped out of line once and got kicked out.

49
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,519
Oh, there's lemonade in the fridge.

50
00:06:36,519 --> 00:06:37,559
Want some?

51
00:06:38,880 --> 00:06:39,519
 I'll get it.

52
00:06:43,280 --> 00:06:43,780
Tang,

53
00:06:44,400 --> 00:06:45,519
how many dishes did you make?

54
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:48,920
What's stressing you out?

55
00:06:50,519 --> 00:06:51,079
So...

56
00:06:53,079 --> 00:06:54,199
