57
00:06:57,880 --> 00:06:58,380
How about this?

58
00:07:01,119 --> 00:07:04,679
You should just move in here for good.

59
00:07:06,400 --> 00:07:07,719
Seriously!

60
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:09,199
I won't be lonely,

61
00:07:09,199 --> 00:07:11,639
