Is that someone from home?

64
00:07:17,199 --> 00:07:17,699
No,

65
00:07:18,199 --> 00:07:18,760
 I don't recognize the number.

66
00:07:19,320 --> 00:07:20,199
Give me a sec.

67
00:07:26,519 --> 00:07:27,019
Hello?

68
00:07:31,719 --> 00:07:32,639
Who was that?

69
00:07:33,239 --> 00:07:33,739
It was...

70
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:34,480
that guy.

71
00:07:35,960 --> 00:07:36,559
Which guy?

72
00:07:38,239 --> 00:07:39,639
The food critic.

73
00:07:42,159 --> 00:07:43,400
He called to apologize.

74
00:07:44,440 --> 00:07:47,920
And he said he has some business to discuss.

75
00:07:49,199 --> 00:07:49,699
Tell you what,

76
00:07:50,239 --> 00:07:51,159
I'm coming with you.

77
00:07:52,559 --> 00:07:53,199
Stay right there.

78
00:07:53,880 --> 00:07:55,960
Wait, why? Oh,

79
00:07:55,960 --> 00:07:58,119
I see... keeping him all to yourself?

80
00:07:58,440 --> 00:07:59,280
In your dreams.

81
00:08:00,119 --> 00:08:01,400
You’re my best friend.

82
00:08:01,960 --> 00:08:02,920
And because of that,

83
00:08:03,119 --> 00:08:05,880
